â”‚                                               for partial matching.          â”‚
â”‚ --tts-speed                          FLOAT    Speech speed multiplier (1.0 = â”‚
â”‚                                               normal, 2.0 = twice as fast,   â”‚
â”‚                                               0.5 = half speed).             â”‚
â”‚                                               [default: 1.0]                 â”‚
